Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:54.71,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君の手を引くその役目が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:20:01.89,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僕の使命だなんて　そう思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:08.02,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}だけど今わかったんだ　僕らならもう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:16.11,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}重ねた日々がほら、導いてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:22.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君が大人になってくその時間が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:28.82,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}降り積もる間に僕も変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:34.85,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}たとえばそこにこんな歌があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:45.55,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ふたりはいつもどんな時もつながっていける
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:20.13,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突然ふいに鳴り響くベルの音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:26.30,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}焦る僕　解ける手　離れてく君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:32.84,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢中で呼び止めて　抱き締めたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:41.81,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君がどこに行ったって僕の声で守るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:49.89,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君が僕の前に現れた日から
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:56.62,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何もかもが違くみえたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:22:02.68,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}朝も光も涙も、歌う声も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:09.21,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君が輝きをくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:16.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}押さえきれない思いをこの声に乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:22.57,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}遠く君の街へ届けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:28.35,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}たとえばそれがこんな歌だったら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:39.16,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ぼくらは何処にいたとしてもつながっていける
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:54.71,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}牵着你的手向前不曾有过迟疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:20:01.89,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我深信那是我与生俱来的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:08.02,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}而现在我已然了解 我们留下的足印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:16.11,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}已化作一盏盏明灯 为我们指引方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:22.17,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}你长大成人的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:28.82,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我也发生着些许的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:34.85,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}假如在你身边有着这样的一首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:45.55,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我俩无论何时何地 都将紧紧相连
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:20.13,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不经意间响彻的铃声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:26.30,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}焦急的我 松开的手 离去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:32.84,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}使尽全力将你叫住 将你抱住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:41.81,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论你身在何方 我的声音都将守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:49.89,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}从你出现在我面前的那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:56.62,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我的世界仿佛焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:22:02.68,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}无论是清晨 光芒 泪水 抑或歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:09.21,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切都因你而闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:16.17,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}让这份难以抑制的思念乘着歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:22.57,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}飞向远方你所在的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:28.35,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}假如那会是一首如此这般的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:39.16,EDCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我们无论身在何处 都能紧紧相连
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你叫出来 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不是做了什么让长谷同学生气的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不明白为什么长谷同学躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得直接去问他本人会比较好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我感觉就算去问他 也得不出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他是不是害怕和你在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.85,0:00:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他把九条当成了自己的一面镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}九条… 同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小学的时候你和九条关系很好对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟现在的长谷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可… 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他也并不认为会发生同样的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不知道还会因为什么原因又让你失去记忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对他来说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的记忆再次消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是他最难忍受的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我完全没明白长谷同学的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}亏我还是长谷同学的朋友呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是 该怎么办才好呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fn腾祥铚谦钢笔简\blur0\bord1\c&H353639&\3c&HFFFFFF&}#12 「请和我做朋友。」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8\3c&H4D7B58&}星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 九条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 得把舞子要的笔记借给她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.56,0:02:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一节就是古典 真累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各小组的代表出来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要决定打扫的地方啰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不准有抱怨 一次定输赢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都说对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是抱怨也没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快点打扫完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我从什么时候开始跟你们同一组了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}座位也很近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近 你们好像有点奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「你们」是在说谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫香织跟你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗 我觉得跟平常没什么不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}落叶装满了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先拿去丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫最近怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有没有跟平常不太一样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看起来很开心 但总觉得在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个人以前明明那么要好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然现在也称不上关系不好就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为什么要躲着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才… 才没有躲着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这点事我还是看得出来的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果是讨厌我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今后也可以不再找你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果讨厌的话 就不会这么烦恼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前说希望桐生同学当我丈夫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉你好像真的生气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先变得奇怪的明明是桐生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之所以不能跟你好好说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是因为我怕再惹你讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不想听到你说什么今后可以不再找我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坦诚道歉的桐生同学 感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要认为自己做错了就会道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平常很少做错事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才没什么机会道歉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我以后还可以一直让你照顾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是多想依赖別人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:06:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那倒是可以 但我可没打算要纵容你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山岸同学好像也变得有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这样子就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家都看得出来你跟藤宫不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 也不是不能理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想只要保持这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟山岸同学她们也变得亲近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在教室里 藤宫同学也不用再伪装自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今后也一定会交到更多朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我为此感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不想再让藤宫同学留下悲伤的回忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为一直以来她都沉浸在悲伤里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你的悲伤就无所谓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说了 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才没有觉得悲伤啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8\3c&H588461&}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难得的寒假 大家一起去哪里玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织想去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我寒假要跟家人一起去旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我爸爸很喜欢旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 大家要玩得开心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实我今年也要跟家人去旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你家有这惯例来着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今年突然下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 这就开始准备年节菜了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今年正月难得能在家里悠闲地过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在就开始准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在只要这样就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天是除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各位观众是否做好过年的准备了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天前来购物的顾客蜂拥而至…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈妈 午饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈妈
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}//（屏字）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:00.68,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H705646&\pos(608,217)\frz11.533}新邮件
Comment: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.43,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H705646&\pos(439,259)}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.52,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H705646&\pos(505,395)\frz13.967}我去听第九交响曲
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}//
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每年除夕都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么可能在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 旅行突然中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家也是爸爸突然接到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}于是今年就在家里悠闲地过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 没想到真的能在这里遇到藤宫同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今天也是 想好了要散步的话一定来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想着可能会遇到长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 刚才的话別放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去年的这时候可想不到会和长谷同学这样走着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时还不在同一个班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是五月十二日来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学第一次跟我打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么突然 吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 一定是很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是那时候还没说过关于记忆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我应该会想着 和我交朋友会给长谷同学添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果长谷同学没有对我说「即便如此也要跟我做朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我现在也肯定还是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的谢谢了 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是想和藤宫同学做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差不多回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去吃可丽饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里的可丽饼这么好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总说要一起来 结果从来没来过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日记上也经常看到这件事 一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过今天就像做梦一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}见到了长谷同学 还能一起吃可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学一直很担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以一直想跟你来尝尝这里的可丽饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好让你稍微放心一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好吃了我再去要一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天谢谢了 还让你陪我走到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学先请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我送你到你家附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里有座神社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上小学的时候路过这里经常去参拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然早了一点 去新年参拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想忘记今天的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天和长谷同学一起度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想全部记住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多小的事也想记住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我更不希望无法跟长谷同学做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果那一天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算能记得长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不会觉得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为… 我想像以前那样聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想像今天这样见面聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想继续和长谷同学做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经不知道该怎么办了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我真是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学流泪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明不想再看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白痴白痴白痴白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我忘记了最重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也一样 还想和藤宫同学更多更多更多地聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要更多更多的时间在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想一直…一直一直一直和藤宫同学做朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是令人放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 既然是和长谷同学在一起 那就跟我说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}您好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织一直不回来 你爸都要报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是你们两个现在这样被你爸撞上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那要叫的就是救护车了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明年也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}彼此彼此
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拥有不愿忘记的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家一起留下的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两人一起留下的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回忆是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 还有更重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是 今后也要继续创造回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我们不断重复
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论几次 都将持续
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做朋友吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 平常都会写些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
